Almost all of the trophies can be earned within an hour except for the high-earner trophies (very hard to obtain 999,999 points through normal gameplay) and the win-count trophies (very tedious to earn 999 wins).

This results in many trophy-less hours of gameplay to complete the game. The highest trophies should remain difficult to obtain, but there may need to be more trophies or activities introduced in order to break up that tedium.